title: (Weds Full) Spill the Tea: Did Someone on the Show Steal From Us? + Bobby on Why You Have a Better Chance of Becoming a Saint Than Winning Powerball + "Were They A President?" Game
itunes:title: (Weds Full) Spill the Tea: Did Someone on the Show Steal From Us? + Bobby on Why You Have a Better Chance of Becoming a Saint Than Winning Powerball + "Were They A President?" Game
description:
Someone gets the tea spilled on them about stealing something from another show member.  Bobby talks about the largest Powerball winners of all time and things you have a better chance of having happen to you than winning. The show tries to identify whether the famous American was ever president or not.
